# Imported world & player data — kept OUT of the core repo on purpose.
# World comes from a separate source (RotS-WorldFiles, or an old server backup
# via scripts/import-world-data.sh); player data is per-deployment and may
# contain PII. None of it is ever committed here.
# (.gitignore does not allow trailing inline comments, so notes go above.)
#   lib/world/    -> rooms, mobs, objects (items), zones, shops, scripts, mudlle
#   lib/players/  -> player account files (A-E/F-J/K-O/P-T/U-Z/ZZZ buckets)
#   lib/plrobjs/  -> per-player saved objects / equipment
#   lib/exploits/ -> per-player exploit-tracking files
#   mobs/         -> scratch dir created by `make setup`
lib/world/
lib/players/
lib/plrobjs/
lib/exploits/
mobs/

